  "slug": "vanilla-expansion-collection",
  "title": "Vanilla Expansion",
  "description": "A modern look of vanilla experience",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://cf.way2muchnoise.eu/versions/847190.svg\" alt=\"title\" />&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Description:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This resource pack is collection of all feature from other modules</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Modules:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>[ <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/better-nature\">Better Nature</a> ] [ <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/player-utilities\">Player Utilities</a> ] [ <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/radiant-redstone\">Radiant Redstone</a> ] [ <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/font-trim\">Font Trim</a> ] [ <a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/scaffolding-delta\">Scaffolding Delta</a> ]</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>All feature implemented:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/VE/global.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"1127\" height=\"634\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Redstone Wire:</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 3d model inspired by&nbsp;</span><a style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/project-red-transmission\" rel=\"nofollow\">ProjectRed</a><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><a style=\"font-size: 18px; background-color: #ffffff;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fmodrinth.com%252fmod%252fredpower2-wiring\" rel=\"nofollow\">RedPower</a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - optimized models and blockstates to support rotation to have only a essential texture</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Redstone Torch ,&nbsp; Repeater , Comparator , Redstone Ores (stone and deepslate) :</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- emit texture &nbsp;<strong>Now without Mod support!</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/radiant%20redstone/screen2.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"380\" height=\"223\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Chorus plant (and flower)&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; - Implemented an optimized version of chorus plants (this isn't the original , only a reimplementation) from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/betterend\"><strong>Better End</strong></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/better%20nature/screen3.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"301\" height=\"248\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">TorchFlower</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;- Added emit light on flower of torch flower</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/better%20nature/screen4.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"312\" height=\"239\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Goat Horns:&nbsp;An updated port from Goat Utils</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - All horns have a custom icon that can define the rarity</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/Goat%20Utils/screen1.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"286\" height=\"92\" /><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/Goat%20Utils/screen.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"102\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Subtitles:&nbsp;An updated port from Warden Gadgets</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Shrieker Subtitles show how many shrieker left after the spawn of warden and some warden stages</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/Warden%20Gadgets/screen.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"488\" height=\"190\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Smithing Template:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- A custom font to allow to see ingredient materials and ingredient of trimming</span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"376\" height=\"329\" /><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen1.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"379\" height=\"154\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Firework ingredients:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- A custom font to allow to see ingredient materials and colors</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen2.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"486\" height=\"435\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Pottery Sherd on Decorative Pots</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; - A custom font to allow to see shards used as item icon</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen3.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"396\" height=\"262\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Banner Pattern icons</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; - A custom font to allow to see colors and pattern used on ANY banner</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen4.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"458\" height=\"224\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Falling Block Damage</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;- A custom font to allow to see the damage (anvil was multiplied on block height)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen5.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"326\" height=\"125\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Poison Damage</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- A custom font to see the damage of poison</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen9.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"429\" height=\"109\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">More intuitive Tooltips</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;- Custom font to allow a view more intuitive on any armor</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen10.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"483\" height=\"192\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Absorption and Regen Hearts</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;- A custom font to see hearts from absorption and regeneration effects from consumable items</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen8.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"451\" height=\"108\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Enchantments Overhal</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;-&nbsp; Any enchantment now show with all valid items to be applied</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen7.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"167\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;- All enchantments with levels now show with \"max level\" tip before the level&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;- All enchantments levels are now colored</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/font%20trim/screen6.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"378\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Scaffolding</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - Small extra shape colored</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Has emit light&nbsp;<strong>Now without Mod support!</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- Define the distance before the fall</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Added CTM support (require&nbsp;<a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/continuity\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Continuity</strong></a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<strong>Optifine</strong>)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://github.com/DevDyna/ContentArchive/blob/main/Vanilla%20Expansion/scaffolding-delta/old/pack/fancy/screen2.png?raw=true\" width=\"553\" height=\"311\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Block Breaking stages</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- changed texture with a more intuitive (see screenshot)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Enchanted Golden Apple</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - changed texture into \"diamond golden apple\"</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Planned Features:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Menu/inventory update? (change all gui into dark mode)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Leaves decay? Better grass model? Easter eggs?&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Logic update? (modify model of comparator and repeater to make more intuitive simil&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/project-red-transmission\" rel=\"nofollow\">ProjectRed</a>&nbsp;but adapted)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Redstone wire power tooltip?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>",
